  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE BAYOU CASOTTE INDUSTRIAL ZONE; TO PROVIDE FOR CERTAIN LEGISLATIVE FINDINGS; TO AMEND SECTION 27-31-1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE THAT IF A MUNICIPALITY CHANGES ITS BOUNDARIES SO AS TO INCLUDE WITHIN THE BOUNDARIES OF THE MUNICIPALITY ANY PORTION OF THE AREA COMPRISING THE BAYOU CASOTTE INDUSTRIAL ZONE, ALL REAL AND PERSONAL PROPERTY THAT IS WITHIN THE ZONE AND WITHIN THE BOUNDARIES OF SUCH MUNICIPALITY SHALL BE EXEMPT FROM AD VALOREM TAXATION; TO BRING FORWARD SECTIONS 21-1-27, 21-1-29, 21-1-31, 21-1-33, 21-1-35, 21-1-37, 21-1-39, 21-1-41 AND 21-1-59, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH ARE SECTIONS OF LAW RELATING TO THE EXTENSION OR CONTRACTION OF MUNICIPAL CORPORATE BOUNDARIES, FOR THE PURPOSES OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
